#: ../../L/lose.rst:5
msgid "lose"
msgstr "lose"

#: ../../L/lose.rst:7
msgid "vi\\."
msgstr "自動詞"

#: ../../L/lose.rst:10
msgid ""
"[very common] To fail. A program loses when it encounters an exceptional "
"condition or fails to work in the expected manner."
msgstr "[非常に一般的] 失敗すること。プログラムは、例外的な状況に遭遇したり、期待どおりに動かなかったりするとloseする。"

#: ../../L/lose.rst:14
msgid "To be exceptionally unesthetic or crocky."
msgstr "並外れて見苦しい、あるいはくだらないこと。"

#: ../../L/lose.rst:17
msgid ""
"Of people, to be obnoxious or unusually stupid (as opposed to ignorant). See"
" also :ref:`deserves-to-lose`\\."
msgstr "人について、(無知というのとは対照的に)不快であるか異常に愚かであること。\\ :ref:`deserves-to-lose`\\ も参照。"

#: ../../L/lose.rst:20
msgid ""
"n\\. Refers to something that is :ref:`losing`\\, especially in the phrases "
"\"That's a lose!\" and \"What a lose!\""
msgstr ""
"名詞 \\ :ref:`losing`\\ なものを指す。特に「That's a lose!(あれはloseだ!)」や「What a "
"lose!(なんてloseだ!)」という言い回しで。"
